{"tid":1948991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話功能組別要人？","createTime":"2020-03-29T10:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T03:10:05.000Z","uid":88140,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7a815841a1198bb12249a71652a703a26a87ef","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"「功能組別就係不公義！投票就等於支持不公義！」<br />\n『你仲投功能組別就會白白浪費咗「人權與民主法案」！』<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你唔認同唔緊要，只需要當佢係一條支線。我地唔可以放過任何一個可以抗衡政府嘅機會，而體制內外嘅抗爭同時進行都得㗎聰明。<br />\n<br />\n功能組別的確係不公義，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過如果我地直接唔玩，咪即係將議會內嘅話事權拱手相讓？</span>立法會廢，係咪就等於唔洗理佢？如果地區直選加玩埋功能組別可以攞到35+，以民意脅逼議員否決所有議案，呢個憲政危機係絕對有機會要脅到政府。<br />\n<br />\n要脅政府做咩嘢，係九月選舉前仲有啲時間可以傾。但要過35+，只靠地區直選係鬥唔過保皇黨配票，一定要玩埋功能組別。我呢啲no stake既社會寄生蟲就冇資格投功能組別，超區留番俾我地投，64比應該唔會輸。希望有票嘅手足可以轉投功能組別，盡攞議席呀！<br />\n<br />\nBTW由超區轉功能組別要係<span style=\"color: red;\">4月2號</span>之前申請，麻煩各位手足做嘢！</span>"},{"pid":"3fd21ab797196b927661d337ea98f1f7c20fc39c","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:53:08.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"93d03903afbfb6f60ed68f4058715bdb940e4c60","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e113d27ad65d2cdebf099f4ed02b301d0ac754f","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be117390ef5196d58dfd832ef17aebde5d7de362","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:53:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b53533f9551aa1fe97e1724297e011ca27afa06","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37444c4c7be6d25670d75d8c878e4da9759033a0","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7254d644ec3de199cf7c388ded1eb15079e620e7","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a09649de6f502155e4e14efcc70bde8645743690","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ccfb441a2f300713f6c51955ac5622377ed12dc","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70f1c374fe1d96d19be3943d4b9e01019c0f4479","tid":1948991,"uid":88140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51d80cdb15e9b61a2562fde0957fa5929f09f911","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c6b7826039ebd26d71bd258645c68809665103","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:04:19.000Z","msg":"醫管局員工陣線<br />\n<br />\n【全面爭奪，加入功能組別】<br />\n <br />\n2019年立法會選舉今年9月即日開打，更新選民資料及新登記成為選民將分別於4月2日和5月2日截止。本會希望同事能盡公民責任，成為選民，於地區直選和衞生服務界及醫學界投票，為自己表態。<br />\n <br />\n步驟如下：<br />\n <br />\n💡查閱你本身是否選民及有否屬於任何功能組別的投票資格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/regulations.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2Fregulations.jsp&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=6758064f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/regulations.jsp</a><br />\n <br />\n👏若你本身已是選民，但屬於超級區議會(區議會(第二))或其他功能組別的選民<br />\n<br />\n更改成為衞生服務界或醫學界選民：(4月2日前)<br />\n填妥REO-43 表格 👉🏻<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-43%28C&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=53d4d050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C</a>).pdf<br />\n <br />\n👋若你本身已是選民，但不屬任何功能組別選民<br />\n<br />\n登記成為衞生服務界或醫學界選民：(4月2日前)<br />\n<br />\n填妥REO-41表格 👉🏻<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=1cd83137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n <br />\n💪若你不是選民，登記成為選民：(5月2日前)<br />\n<br />\n填妥REO-1表格 👉🏻<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Feform%2FREO-1%28C&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=628d56f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C</a>)_eSign.pdf<br />\n <br />\n💡遞交表格方法<br />\n1.於選舉事務處電子表格平台上傳：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Findex.jsp&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=a880a080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp</a><br />\n2.電郵至form@reo.gov.hk<br />\n3.郵遞方式寄回九龍九龍灣展貿徑一號九龍灣國際展貿中心十三樓<br />\n4.傳真至 2891 1180<br />\n <br />\n💡若以手機/平版電腦填寫表格，可以下載「Adobe Fill &amp; Sign」App。<br />\n💡若以Apple 電腦填寫，可以參考以下連結來於網上進行簽署(signature)動作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-hk/guide/preview/prvw35725/mac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-hk%2Fguide%2Fpreview%2Fprvw35725%2Fmac&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=ea782e0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/en-hk/guide/preview/prvw35725/mac</a><br />\n <br />\n功能組別的選民資格要求：<br />\n衞生服務界：<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/hs_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fhs_c.pdf&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=6e24f41d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/hs_c.pdf</a> (P.9 附錄乙)<br />\n醫學界：<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/med_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fmed_c.pdf&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=69ed0e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/med_c.pdf</a> (P.9 附錄乙)<br />\n <br />\n兄弟爬山，全面爭奪所有戰線，<br />\n對守舊過時的代議士說不，<br />\n用選票作表態，<br />\n力求於時代變革中尋求希望。<br />\n<br />\n好好的投，好好的活下去。"},{"pid":"6ce0dce1903c9bda3bba3c525ac76ca6981f2b08","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b314006e33b4bafe045f8a4ad288ea804ca95d1","tid":1948991,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"投唔投個選舉都繼續,咪俾保皇黨自動當選囉"},{"pid":"424b543b315e7ba49f6524c54c38a2d96c122e53","tid":1948991,"uid":345458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"Too long didn&rsquo;t read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab671e1e45226977ae3d901803af4c8eb0479d0","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0817164975786d6b13194a7fc62be51b55cbe9d1","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dea369f418cb061653b35738ed4b532e2273d70","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"739d852e54d3467cbb084e7e312eb81f893b44d3","tid":1948991,"uid":238461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:23:42.000Z","msg":"幫你推下，不過個標題睇到我好亂。"},{"pid":"1b9fcfc98fa8795b6045551d9ae8921a8d22d366","tid":1948991,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"白票兵不願面對"},{"pid":"4ad3809eecb4c8ec343e494fd887cd45f5f372bf","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"a5a555c6183a204c24cc31db3831237bc0d5f3a1","tid":1948991,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e058c26c18c2f30527e920df7f167d56d68e9b1e","tid":1948991,"uid":111495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"Agger 手足辛苦了"},{"pid":"e6825a40fcd955b5d1a5a472636c79ea7f571744","tid":1948991,"uid":92804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊要超區定要功能組別。。。"}]}